<description>&lt;p align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;f16&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;INS上迷倒万千少女的大爷，有颜有肉还有钱，60岁的他活出了所有男人梦想的样子！&lt;br/&gt;当国内的女生还在花痴舔屏小鲜肉的时候，&lt;br/&gt;国外的一位大爷却在INS上悄然走红，&lt;br/&gt;迷倒了万千少女。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;img os-data=&quot;http://a.ad/bl0ck.jpg&quot; data-link=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/image/MMZHk7&quot; ess-data=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/images/2020/04/10/0wx_fmtpng20af7e21e4bed3fd.jpg&quot;/&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;看这完美的身材，&lt;br/&gt;你能相信他已经60岁了吗？&lt;br/&gt;小IN知道的时候也是震惊的，&lt;br/&gt;这明明就是40岁的帅大叔嘛！&lt;br/&gt;&lt;img os-data=&quot;http://a.ad/bl0ck.jpg&quot; data-link=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/image/MMZYYJ&quot; ess-data=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/images/2020/04/10/0wx_fmtjpeg89d2665035edb992.jpg&quot;/&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;比起小鲜肉稚嫩的脸庞，&lt;br/&gt;经过岁月沉淀的他&lt;br/&gt;反而更加魅力十足。&lt;br/&gt;有型的头发，不羁的胡须，&lt;br/&gt;蓝色的眼睛看得小IN都不好意思了呢。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;img os-data=&quot;http://a.ad/bl0ck.jpg&quot; data-link=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/image/MMZWoh&quot; ess-data=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/images/2020/04/10/0wx_fmtjpeg2d6f8cce43d985ce.jpg&quot;/&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;大爷名叫Jack Guy，&lt;br/&gt;喜欢在INS分享自己的日常，&lt;br/&gt;他有格调有品位的生活，&lt;br/&gt;引得粉丝们直呼羡慕嫉妒。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;img os-data=&quot;http://a.ad/bl0ck.jpg&quot; data-link=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/image/MMZOvy&quot; ess-data=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/images/2020/04/10/0wx_fmtjpege4f3167f20d9f286.jpg&quot;/&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Jack拥有一幢海边别墅，&lt;br/&gt;简洁大方的装修风格透露出主人的好品味，&lt;br/&gt;大大的落地窗和观景阳台拥有无敌视野，&lt;br/&gt;可以感受每天的晨与昏。&lt;br/&gt;▼&lt;br/&gt;&lt;img os-data=&quot;http://a.ad/bl0ck.jpg&quot; data-link=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/image/MMbFUu&quot; ess-data=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/images/2020/04/10/0wx_fmtjpeg5b08448799a811a7.jpg&quot;/&gt; &lt;br/&gt;&lt;img os-data=&quot;http://a.ad/bl0ck.jpg&quot; data-link=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/image/MMZPaR&quot; ess-data=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/images/2020/04/10/0wx_fmtjpegbe6e8c205634a235.jpg&quot;/&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;每天出门的代步工具是炫酷的机车，&lt;br/&gt;黑色的机车皮衣加墨镜，&lt;br/&gt;简直不要太拉风！&lt;br/&gt;▼&lt;br/&gt;&lt;img os-data=&quot;http://a.ad/bl0ck.jpg&quot; data-link=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/image/MMZwiV&quot; ess-data=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/images/2020/04/10/0wx_fmtjpeg519206490a6accd1.jpg&quot;/&gt; &lt;br/&gt;&lt;img os-data=&quot;http://a.ad/bl0ck.jpg&quot; data-link=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/image/MMbuQF&quot; ess-data=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/images/2020/04/10/0wx_fmtpng69e6eaf6bf9e3b90.jpg&quot;/&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;还拥有一辆个性十足的跑车，&lt;br/&gt;不时和朋友去玩漂移，&lt;br/&gt;体验一下肾上腺素狂飙的速度与激情&lt;br/&gt;▼&lt;br/&gt;&lt;img os-data=&quot;http://a.ad/bl0ck.jpg&quot; data-link=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/image/MMblng&quot; ess-data=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/images/2020/04/10/0wx_fmtpnga2c4e04c5e6c093e.jpg&quot;/&gt; &lt;br/&gt;&lt;img os-data=&quot;http://a.ad/bl0ck.jpg&quot; data-link=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/image/MMbJiY&quot; ess-data=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/images/2020/04/10/0wx_fmtpngee5ef5f579070ed6.jpg&quot;/&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;兴致来了便驾驶越野车，&lt;br/&gt;行驶在山间峡谷，&lt;br/&gt;感受大自然的神秘和狂野。&lt;br/&gt;▼&lt;br/&gt;&lt;img os-data=&quot;http://a.ad/bl0ck.jpg&quot; data-link=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/image/MMbMCz&quot; ess-data=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/images/2020/04/10/0wx_fmtjpeg005b04a3e61c3192.jpg&quot;/&gt; &lt;br/&gt;&lt;img os-data=&quot;http://a.ad/bl0ck.jpg&quot; data-link=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/image/MMbxYI&quot; ess-data=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/images/2020/04/10/0wx_fmtjpeg726532137da5d01d.jpg&quot;/&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;还有自己的私人游艇，&lt;br/&gt;一个人出海感受海风的湿润，&lt;br/&gt;或是召集朋友来个游艇轰趴。&lt;br/&gt;▼&lt;br/&gt;&lt;img os-data=&quot;http://a.ad/bl0ck.jpg&quot; data-link=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/image/MMbmxX&quot; ess-data=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/images/2020/04/10/0wx_fmtjpeg8d23606e7097daee.jpg&quot;/&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;你以为这些就完了，&lt;br/&gt;NO NO NO!&lt;br/&gt;大爷还拥有自己的私人飞机，&lt;br/&gt;随时任性来一场说走就走的旅行，&lt;br/&gt;而且连开飞机这种技术活都是自己亲自上阵！&lt;br/&gt;▼&lt;br/&gt;&lt;img os-data=&quot;http://a.ad/bl0ck.jpg&quot; data-link=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/image/MMb9Cp&quot; ess-data=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/images/2020/04/10/0wx_fmtjpeg5b02fd80485490a2.jpg&quot;/&gt; &lt;br/&gt;&lt;img os-data=&quot;http://a.ad/bl0ck.jpg&quot; data-link=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/image/MMbLmN&quot; ess-data=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/images/2020/04/10/0wx_fmtjpegcab8f5e363b09ba5.jpg&quot;/&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;炫酷的大爷不仅有钱，&lt;br/&gt;人家还是超级有名的摄影师，&lt;br/&gt;拍的照片可都是杂志封面级别的！&lt;br/&gt;&lt;img os-data=&quot;http://a.ad/bl0ck.jpg&quot; data-link=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/image/MMbRvP&quot; ess-data=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/images/2020/04/10/0wx_fmtjpegfbf6c4b9ae0872a6.jpg&quot;/&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;玩摄影的男人都最帅，&lt;br/&gt;这姿势一看就很专业！&lt;br/&gt;▼&lt;br/&gt;&lt;img os-data=&quot;http://a.ad/bl0ck.jpg&quot; data-link=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/image/MMbSaQ&quot; ess-data=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/images/2020/04/10/0wx_fmtjpeg97e505827fbd3e21.jpg&quot;/&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;坚持每天拍摄日出，&lt;br/&gt;366天从不间断，&lt;br/&gt;果然是有生活情调的人。&lt;br/&gt;▼&lt;br/&gt;&lt;img os-data=&quot;http://a.ad/bl0ck.jpg&quot; data-link=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/image/MMbKUB&quot; ess-data=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/images/2020/04/10/0wx_fmtjpeg385efc2bf533f3c6.jpg&quot;/&gt; &lt;br/&gt;&lt;img os-data=&quot;http://a.ad/bl0ck.jpg&quot; data-link=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/image/MMbqxU&quot; ess-data=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/images/2020/04/10/0wx_fmtjpeg411c69302c285759.jpg&quot;/&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;出去旅游的时候&lt;br/&gt;用心记录下每个美好瞬间。&lt;br/&gt;▼&lt;br/&gt;&lt;img os-data=&quot;http://a.ad/bl0ck.jpg&quot; data-link=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/image/MMbZm6&quot; ess-data=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/images/2020/04/10/0wx_fmtpngba470199f2e4960b.jpg&quot;/&gt; &lt;br/&gt;&lt;img os-data=&quot;http://a.ad/bl0ck.jpg&quot; data-link=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/image/MMbXwk&quot; ess-data=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/images/2020/04/10/0wx_fmtjpege6969e1936c3c6e5.jpg&quot;/&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;除了日常的风光摄影，&lt;br/&gt;Jack也喜欢人物拍摄，&lt;br/&gt;《黑客帝国》的主演Keanu Reeves ，&lt;br/&gt;《绝望主妇》的主演 Eva Longoria&lt;br/&gt;等明星都曾成为他的拍摄对象。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;img os-data=&quot;http://a.ad/bl0ck.jpg&quot; data-link=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/image/MMbCQj&quot; ess-data=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/images/2020/04/10/0wx_fmtpnga4023e508b439dc3.jpg&quot;/&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Jack善于捕捉细节，&lt;br/&gt;他拍的黑白人物照，&lt;br/&gt;眼神里满满都是情绪和故事。&lt;br/&gt;▼&lt;br/&gt;&lt;img os-data=&quot;http://a.ad/bl0ck.jpg&quot; data-link=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/image/MMbbyq&quot; ess-data=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/images/2020/04/10/0wx_fmtjpegf9a8bf8d6b7ac5e6.jpg&quot;/&gt; &lt;br/&gt;&lt;img os-data=&quot;http://a.ad/bl0ck.jpg&quot; data-link=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/image/MMbNEG&quot; ess-data=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/images/2020/04/10/0wx_fmtjpeg8c7f41a44957314d.jpg&quot;/&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;给模特拍时尚大片也驾轻就熟，&lt;br/&gt;有自己独特的风格&lt;br/&gt;▼&lt;br/&gt;&lt;img os-data=&quot;http://a.ad/bl0ck.jpg&quot; data-link=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/image/MMbcw3&quot; ess-data=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/images/2020/04/10/0wx_fmtpng1e95f1e47b87cacc.jpg&quot;/&gt; &lt;br/&gt;&lt;img os-data=&quot;http://a.ad/bl0ck.jpg&quot; data-link=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/image/MMbzd0&quot; ess-data=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/images/2020/04/10/0wx_fmtpngdaea94bb42f6a31b.jpg&quot;/&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;连有名的GQ，LATINA等杂志也和他约片，&lt;br/&gt;他的摄影作品多次登上了杂志封面和内页&lt;br/&gt;▼&lt;br/&gt;&lt;img os-data=&quot;http://a.ad/bl0ck.jpg&quot; data-link=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/image/MMbDqZ&quot; ess-data=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/images/2020/04/10/0wx_fmtpnge5afd33c6bcd9a70.jpg&quot;/&gt; &lt;br/&gt;&lt;img os-data=&quot;http://a.ad/bl0ck.jpg&quot; data-link=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/image/MMbvN9&quot; ess-data=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/images/2020/04/10/0wx_fmtjpega3f8934d6750b846.jpg&quot;/&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;这和他曾今的经历密不可分，&lt;br/&gt;年轻时的他也是一名模特，&lt;br/&gt;所以他在拍摄时知道怎样与模特沟通，&lt;br/&gt;如何调动模特的情绪，&lt;br/&gt;最终拍出自己想要的效果。&lt;br/&gt;▼&lt;br/&gt;&lt;img os-data=&quot;http://a.ad/bl0ck.jpg&quot; data-link=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/image/MMbVUn&quot; ess-data=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/images/2020/04/10/0wx_fmtjpeg82ac190cce0a1a99.jpg&quot;/&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;因为当模特的经历和现在摄影师的身份，&lt;br/&gt;Jack虽然已年过六旬，&lt;br/&gt;却依然活跃在美国时尚圈。&lt;br/&gt;▼&lt;br/&gt;&lt;img os-data=&quot;http://a.ad/bl0ck.jpg&quot; data-link=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/image/MMbyQH&quot; ess-data=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/images/2020/04/10/0wx_fmtjpeg577617631854407a.jpg&quot;/&gt; &lt;br/&gt;&lt;img os-data=&quot;http://a.ad/bl0ck.jpg&quot; data-link=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/image/MMb1JJ&quot; ess-data=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/images/2020/04/10/0wx_fmtjpeg105b3ff101f816d6.jpg&quot;/&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Jack大爷的朋友圈阵容那不是一般豪华，&lt;br/&gt;横跨演艺界，模特界甚至歌手界，&lt;br/&gt;维密超模Gigi Hadid，歌手Michael Ray&lt;br/&gt;等都和他私交甚好&lt;br/&gt;▼&lt;br/&gt;&lt;img os-data=&quot;http://a.ad/bl0ck.jpg&quot; data-link=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/image/MMbhy7&quot; ess-data=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/images/2020/04/10/0wx_fmtjpegdcdbd762c7289fd4.jpg&quot;/&gt; &lt;br/&gt;&lt;img os-data=&quot;http://a.ad/bl0ck.jpg&quot; data-link=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/image/MMbsGR&quot; ess-data=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/images/2020/04/10/0wx_fmtjpegd61989809c8113be.jpg&quot;/&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;而他本人也曾多次登上时尚杂志封面，&lt;br/&gt;Men's Health更是对他做了专题报道，&lt;br/&gt;特地放上他20年前的照片对比，&lt;br/&gt;盛赞他的身材竟保持得如此完美。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;img os-data=&quot;http://a.ad/bl0ck.jpg&quot; data-link=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/image/MMb2Eh&quot; ess-data=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/images/2020/04/10/0wx_fmtjpega3859a9f31c8d4ae.jpg&quot;/&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;确实，看着他完美的人鱼线和八块腹肌，&lt;br/&gt;你很难把他和任何年老的词汇联系到一起，&lt;br/&gt;而这一切都来自于他几十年如一日的坚持锻炼。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;img os-data=&quot;http://a.ad/bl0ck.jpg&quot; data-link=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/image/MMb3qa&quot; ess-data=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/images/2020/04/10/0wx_fmtjpegdcfe1d97e14ce35d.jpg&quot;/&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;运动已经融入他的生活成为一种习惯，&lt;br/&gt;房间里摆放了很多的器材，&lt;br/&gt;健身是他每天必不可少的功课，&lt;br/&gt;各种支撑和拉伸训练，&lt;br/&gt;才造就了他一身健硕的肌肉。&lt;br/&gt;▼&lt;br/&gt;&lt;img os-data=&quot;http://a.ad/bl0ck.jpg&quot; data-link=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/image/MMbody&quot; ess-data=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/images/2020/04/10/0wx_fmtjpegc01f9727e0903774.jpg&quot;/&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Jack还养成了规律作息的习惯，&lt;br/&gt;每天早上迎着晨光熹微，&lt;br/&gt;独自到到海边跑步，&lt;br/&gt;帅气的承包了整片沙滩。&lt;br/&gt;▼&lt;br/&gt;&lt;img os-data=&quot;http://a.ad/bl0ck.jpg&quot; data-link=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/image/MMb4eV&quot; ess-data=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/images/2020/04/10/0wx_fmtjpeg0999e331f3e94665.jpg&quot;/&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;中午抽空去海里游个泳，&lt;br/&gt;潜水什么的也完全难不倒他，&lt;br/&gt;那些在泳池里蹦跶的比起大爷来简直弱爆了&lt;br/&gt;▼&lt;br/&gt;&lt;img os-data=&quot;http://a.ad/bl0ck.jpg&quot; data-link=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/image/MMb82N&quot; ess-data=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/images/2020/04/10/0wx_fmtpng75309996b9b86d0a.jpg&quot;/&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;还请了专门的瑜伽教练，&lt;br/&gt;下午来一组瑜伽，&lt;br/&gt;舒展一下筋骨，&lt;br/&gt;享受内心的宁静平和&lt;br/&gt;▼&lt;br/&gt;&lt;img os-data=&quot;http://a.ad/bl0ck.jpg&quot; data-link=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/image/MMbUNg&quot; ess-data=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/images/2020/04/10/0wx_fmtjpeg2f5bece6c47c3b6e.jpg&quot;/&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;除了这些常规的训练，&lt;br/&gt;Jack还喜欢各种各样的户外运动，&lt;br/&gt;潜水，徒步，冲浪，登山，&lt;br/&gt;简直堪称十项全能。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;img os-data=&quot;http://a.ad/bl0ck.jpg&quot; data-link=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/image/MMbTFu&quot; ess-data=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/images/2020/04/10/0wx_fmtpng340b9dc82a1ff5c8.jpg&quot;/&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;山高人为峰，&lt;br/&gt;张开胳膊拥抱初生的朝阳&lt;br/&gt;▼&lt;br/&gt;&lt;img os-data=&quot;http://a.ad/bl0ck.jpg&quot; data-link=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/image/MMbgHF&quot; ess-data=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/images/2020/04/10/0wx_fmtjpegfbe2914608d6cbb0.jpg&quot;/&gt; &lt;br/&gt;&lt;img os-data=&quot;http://a.ad/bl0ck.jpg&quot; data-link=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/image/MMbesz&quot; ess-data=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/images/2020/04/10/0wx_fmtjpeg73b31c01bd315e4c.jpg&quot;/&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;这样身手矫健的大爷，&lt;br/&gt;简直帅爆了！&lt;br/&gt;▼&lt;br/&gt;&lt;img os-data=&quot;http://a.ad/bl0ck.jpg&quot; data-link=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/image/MMbadP&quot; ess-data=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/images/2020/04/10/0wx_fmtjpegb4d8c716fb950f5c.jpg&quot;/&gt; &lt;br/&gt;&lt;img os-data=&quot;http://a.ad/bl0ck.jpg&quot; data-link=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/image/MMb7eY&quot; ess-data=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/images/2020/04/10/0wx_fmtjpeg0c526cc212499ebf.jpg&quot;/&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;乘风破浪，&lt;br/&gt;做一个勇敢的弄潮儿&lt;br/&gt;▼&lt;br/&gt;&lt;img os-data=&quot;http://a.ad/bl0ck.jpg&quot; data-link=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/image/MMb6JI&quot; ess-data=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/images/2020/04/10/0wx_fmtjpeg2f93c04189193c88.jpg&quot;/&gt; &lt;br/&gt;&lt;img os-data=&quot;http://a.ad/bl0ck.jpg&quot; data-link=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/image/MMbpGQ&quot; ess-data=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/images/2020/04/10/0wx_fmtjpeg0bcd2be9aaff4c12.jpg&quot;/&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;攀岩走壁，&lt;br/&gt;挑战自己身体和心理的极限&lt;br/&gt;▼&lt;br/&gt;&lt;img os-data=&quot;http://a.ad/bl0ck.jpg&quot; data-link=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/image/MMbtDX&quot; ess-data=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/images/2020/04/10/0wx_fmtpngebc812de2544cfd4.jpg&quot;/&gt; &lt;br/&gt;&lt;img os-data=&quot;http://a.ad/bl0ck.jpg&quot; data-link=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/image/MMbYFB&quot; ess-data=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/images/2020/04/10/0wx_fmtpng0e055191ba97de25.jpg&quot;/&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;策马扬鞭，&lt;br/&gt;感受肆意奔腾的畅快&lt;br/&gt;▼&lt;br/&gt;&lt;img os-data=&quot;http://a.ad/bl0ck.jpg&quot; data-link=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/image/MMbEAk&quot; ess-data=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/images/2020/04/10/0wx_fmtjpeg4b8334a46fde261b.jpg&quot;/&gt; &lt;br/&gt;&lt;img os-data=&quot;http://a.ad/bl0ck.jpg&quot; data-link=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/image/MMzlL0&quot; ess-data=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/images/2020/04/10/0wx_fmtpng20f7da9e670e133f.jpg&quot;/&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Jack还结交了许多志同道合的朋友，&lt;br/&gt;业余生活同样丰盈而充实。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;img os-data=&quot;http://a.ad/bl0ck.jpg&quot; data-link=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/image/MMbHsp&quot; ess-data=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/images/2020/04/10/0wx_fmtjpega29c72ea2ad18e59.jpg&quot;/&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;和朋友喝个悠闲的下午茶&lt;br/&gt;▼&lt;br/&gt;&lt;img os-data=&quot;http://a.ad/bl0ck.jpg&quot; data-link=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/image/MMbwpq&quot; ess-data=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/images/2020/04/10/0wx_fmtjpeg81d3d89c15a1afcc.jpg&quot;/&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;去海滩上遛遛狗&lt;br/&gt;▼&lt;br/&gt;&lt;img os-data=&quot;http://a.ad/bl0ck.jpg&quot; data-link=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/image/MMbOHj&quot; ess-data=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/images/2020/04/10/0wx_fmtjpegbb9f6c2d5f41c1f2.jpg&quot;/&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;听一场枪与玫瑰的演唱会，&lt;br/&gt;在人群中尽情狂欢，&lt;br/&gt;谁说摇滚只属于年轻人&lt;br/&gt;▼&lt;br/&gt;&lt;img os-data=&quot;http://a.ad/bl0ck.jpg&quot; data-link=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/image/MMbfKG&quot; ess-data=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/images/2020/04/10/0wx_fmtpnga05937978ed5d37b.jpg&quot;/&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;随时来个炫酷的自拍，&lt;br/&gt;上传到社交网络&lt;br/&gt;▼&lt;br/&gt;&lt;img os-data=&quot;http://a.ad/bl0ck.jpg&quot; data-link=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/image/MMbn26&quot; ess-data=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/images/2020/04/10/0wx_fmtpng65348979ad0f85a7.jpg&quot;/&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;还加入了一些俱乐部，&lt;br/&gt;一起将运动进行到底&lt;br/&gt;▼&lt;br/&gt;&lt;img os-data=&quot;http://a.ad/bl0ck.jpg&quot; data-link=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/image/MMzMgZ&quot; ess-data=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/images/2020/04/10/0wx_fmtjpegdb9035923df87b40.jpg&quot;/&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;有颜值有身材有态度，&lt;br/&gt;认真生活的Jack Guy,&lt;br/&gt;活出了所有男人梦想的样子！&lt;br/&gt;▼&lt;br/&gt;&lt;img os-data=&quot;http://a.ad/bl0ck.jpg&quot; data-link=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/image/MMz0DU&quot; ess-data=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/images/2020/04/10/0wx_fmtpng6d8f6534a022d9e4.jpg&quot;/&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;我们无法让青春的容颜永驻，&lt;br/&gt;但我们可以选择拥有健康的体魄，&lt;br/&gt;和一颗乐观年轻的心，&lt;br/&gt;希望你我的60岁，&lt;br/&gt;也能活得像Jack一样精彩！&lt;br/&gt;&lt;img os-data=&quot;http://a.ad/bl0ck.jpg&quot; data-link=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/image/MMzxFn&quot; ess-data=&quot;https://www.privacypic.com/images/2020/04/10/0wx_fmtpng08ae0f3048133ec9.jpg&quot;/&gt; &lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
